<figureCitation box="[528,623,1995,2020]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="3.[151,250,1322,1344]" captionTargetBox="[170,1421,276,1289]" captionTargetId="figure@3.[151,1436,267,1301]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="FIGURE 1. Habitus and aedeagus of Drogo stalsi gen. et. sp. n. Dorsal (A) ventral (B) left lateral (C) and (D) frontal views of aedeagus." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/255042/files/figure.png" pageId="4" pageNumber="494">Figure 1</figureCitation>
